game.name: Car model dress up
game.description:
Hey ladies! The gorgeous car model is waiting for you in this brand girls game. The lady has recently got a big ad assignment and she needs your fashion advice to get ready. A new car has just been introduced to the market and the owner of the car company has chosen this cute model to be appeared in an advertisement where the promotion of car takes place. The cute girl has approached you for the valuable fashion advice. Join Car Model and be prepared to help her to pick up the awesome outfits!
Start it by giving your girl a nice hairstyle and then pair it with a lovely matching dress! Choose an elegant bun, a ponytail or some loose curls for her hair! She would look awesome in any out of outfit options including a strapless red dress with a bit of ruffled around the waist, a long orange outfit with a bit of glitter or a strapless silver mini dress covered in sequins. Her wardrobe will also show you an option of a lovely mini skirt and a crop top inspired by the car races. 
Combine her dress with a pair of matching elegant shoes, printed stockings, some precious jewelry, a nice headband and big bow in her hair! Try to challenge your fashion abilities to the best to make her look like a gorgeous model! Her wardrobe is full of multiple skirts, shorts, halter tops and shoes so you can easily spot the items that will be enough to allow her to attend this popular auto show today. Good luck to create a jaw-dropping look for the girl for this event! Check out more girl-based games and have fun for free, no download required on atmegame.com!
